              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "٤٥١. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): زُهْدُكَ فِي"
            }
          ]
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:310:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/451/571",
        "text": [
          " رَاغِبٍ فِيكَ نُقْصَانُ حَظٍّ، وَرَغْبَتُكَ فِي زَاهِدٍ فِيكَ ذُلُّ نَفْسٍ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "451. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: Your turning away from him who inclines towards you is a loss of your share of advantage while your inclining towards him who turns away from you is humiliation for yourself."
          ]
        }
